{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "vulgate:numbers.27",
    "translationId": "vulgate",
    "bookSlug": "numbers",
    "chapterNumber": 27,
    "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27",
    "summary": "Source text for Numbers 27 in Clementine Vulgate."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.1",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:1",
      "text": "Accesserunt autem filiæ Salphaad, filii Hepher, filii Galaad, filii Machir, filii Manasse, qui fuit filius Joseph: quarum sunt nomina, Maala, et Noa, et Hegla, et Melcha, et Thersa.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.2",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:2",
      "text": "Steteruntque coram Moyse et Eleazaro sacerdote et cunctis principibus populi ad ostium tabernaculi fœderis, atque dixerunt:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.3",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:3",
      "text": "Pater noster mortuus est in deserto, nec fuit in seditione, quæ concitata est contra Dominum sub Core, sed in peccato suo mortuus est: hic non habuit mares filios. Cur tollitur nomen illius de familia sua, quia non habuit filium? date nobis possessionem inter cognatos patris nostri.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.4",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:4",
      "text": "Retulitque Moyses causam earum ad judicium Domini.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.5",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:5",
      "text": "Qui dixit ad eum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.6",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:6",
      "text": "Justam rem postulant filiæ Salphaad: da eis possessionem inter cognatos patris sui, et ei in hæreditatem succedant.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.7",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:7",
      "text": "Ad filios autem Israël loqueris hæc:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.8",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:8",
      "text": "Homo cum mortuus fuerit absque filio, ad filiam ejus transibit hæreditas.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.9",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:9",
      "text": "Si filiam non habuerit, habebit successores fratres suos.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.10",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:10",
      "text": "Quod si et fratres non fuerint, dabitis hæreditatem fratribus patris ejus.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.11",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:11",
      "text": "Sin autem nec patruos habuerit, dabitur hæreditas his qui ei proximi sunt. Eritque hoc filiis Israël sanctum lege perpetua, sicut præcepit Dominus Moysi.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.12",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:12",
      "text": "Dixit quoque Dominus ad Moysen: Ascende in montem istum Abarim, et contemplare inde terram, quam daturus sum filiis Israël.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.13",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:13",
      "text": "Cumque videris eam, ibis et tu ad populum tuum, sicut ivit frater tuus Aaron:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.14",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:14",
      "text": "quia offendistis me in deserto Sin in contradictione multitudinis, nec sanctificare me voluistis coram ea super aquas. Hæ sunt aquæ contradictionis in Cades deserti Sin.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.15",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:15",
      "text": "Cui respondit Moyses:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.16",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:16",
      "text": "Provideat Dominus Deus spirituum omnis carnis hominem, qui sit super multitudinem hanc:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.17",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:17",
      "text": "et possit exire et intrare ante eos, et educere eos vel introducere: ne sit populus Domini sicut oves absque pastore.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.18",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:18",
      "text": "Dixitque Dominus ad eum: Tolle Josue filium Nun, virum in quo est spiritus, et pone manum tuam super eum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.19",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:19",
      "text": "Qui stabit coram Eleazaro sacerdote et omni multitudine:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.20",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:20",
      "text": "et dabis ei præcepta cunctis videntibus, et partem gloriæ tuæ, ut audiat eum omnis synagoga filiorum Israël.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.21",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:21",
      "text": "Pro hoc, si quid agendum erit, Eleazar sacerdos consulet Dominum. Ad verbum ejus egredietur et ingredietur ipse, et omnes filii Israël cum eo, et cetera multitudo.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.22",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:22",
      "text": "Fecit Moyses ut præceperat Dominus: cumque tulisset Josue, statuit eum coram Eleazaro sacerdote et omni frequentia populi.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.27.23",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 27,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 27:23",
      "text": "Et impositis capiti ejus manibus, cuncta replicavit quæ mandaverat Dominus.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
